firstappearance: (Victor Strange) Dr. Strange: Sorcerer Supreme #10 (1989); (Baron Blood) Dr. Strange: Sorcerer Supreme #15 (1990); (Khiron) Dr. Strange: Sorcerer Supreme #10 (1993)
knownrelatives: Eugene Strange (father), Beverley Strange (mother), Donna Strange (sister), all deceased; Dr. Stephen Strange (brother), Clea (sister-in-law)
powers: Victor possesses many standard vampire abilities, including superhuman strength, speed, reflexes, and durability. Knives and bullets cause only superficial surface injury, and he heals swiftly.
